			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="To trigger:&#xD;&#xA;Recruit Shadowheart (From debug book or otherwise)&#xD;&#xA;Recon: oe qnight NIGHT_ShadowHeart_Box_2de162ec-4272-4750-945f-9d306c5ba0da&#xD;&#xA;Go to camp" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="230" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Shadowheart examines the mysterious puzzle box that she's been closely guarding. She has a mission to deliver this item to her cloister in Baldur's Gate, though doesn't truly know what it is. She tries to understand it, and possibly draws the attention of one of her companions - she shuts them down when they ask her about it, however. Note: a version this scene may have already occurred in the Druid Grove - this is a fallback that occurs at the party's campsite." />
